<HEADLINE> HK Chief Executive Meets Foreign Minister Tang </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Chief Executive Tung Chee Hwa
of the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (SAR) of China
Monday evening met with Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan, and hosted
a dinner in his honor.
</P>
<P>
Tang arrived in Hong Kong Monday evening after attending the
fifth ASEAN Regional Forum held in Manila and visiting the
Philippines and Malaysia. He will leave for Beijing Tuesday
morning.
