Tung learnt that the Central Government had raised the issue
with the Indonesian Government repeatedly through diplomatic
channels and had requested the Indonesian Government to
investigate the violence thoroughly in order to prevent similar
incidents from occurring again.
</P>
<P>
Tang and Tung also reviewed the latest economic situation in
the ASEAN countries and Japan, and their future outlook. 
