program, which is expected to create at least 37,000 jobs to
support capacity building for technology and investment services
and sustainable livelihood at community levels. It will cost
16.6 million Dollars.
</P>
<P>
Others are the sustainable agriculture, environment and rural
development program, the national management of social
development and social-economic program.
</P>
