<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Malaysia's ruling United
Malays National Organization (UMNO) Youth Monday proposed that
Malaysia suspend all fresh bilateral dealings with neighboring
Singapore until the latter states its official stand on
outstanding issues with Malaysia.
