<TEXT>
<P>
KINSHASA, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Intense shootings were heard
from the area of this capital city, where the presidential Marble
Palace is located, overnight Saturday.
</P>
<P>
Sources said that troops from two camps in the capital city
were attacking the presidential palace. But the details on what
was going on was not clear immediately.
</P>
