biological study. The prince and his delegation in this current
China tour is to carry out studies on the wide and domestic fowls
in southwest China's Yunnan Province. The delegation will also
inspect the folklore in the province where dozens of ethnic
minorities live in compact community.
</P>
<P>
The prince and his party are expected to leave Beijing for
Yunnan later this evening.  
