<P>
Schumacher had his worst qualifying performance of the season
and started the race in ninth place. He eventually finished fifth
in the German Grand Prix.
</P>
<P>
David Coulthard, Hakkinen's McLaren teammate, finished second
in the race, followed by defending world champion Jacques
Villeneuve of Canada in the third place. 
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
