<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Open Lower </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, August 3 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks lost 201.57
points, or 2.54 percent, to hit 7,734.63 in the first two minutes
of trading on Monday.
</P>
<P>
The key Hang Seng Index rose 30.04 points, or 0.38 percent, to
close at 7,936.20 on Friday. 
